  <summary date="2019-10-18T10:42:51Z" status="Introduced in Senate">National Criminal Justice Commission Act of 2019

This bill establishes the National Criminal Justice Commission. The commission must conduct a comprehensive review of the criminal justice system; make recommendations for criminal justice reform; and disseminate findings and guidance to the federal government and to state, local, and tribal governments.</summary>
